official_title: Testing Message Modality of Culturally Appropriate Nutrition Communication for Mexican American Women
inclusion_criteria:
* Self-identify as Latina or Hispanic
* Self-identify as a woman
* Self-reported as being of age between 18-29 years
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
Must have maximum age of 29 Years
exclusion_criteria: * Not Mexican American (defined as having at least 1 grandparent born in Mexico or self-identifying as Mexican or Mexican American)
